{"tid":648414,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"跪求樂理高手","createTime":"2018-04-30T16:08:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T14:45:09.000Z","uid":96561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9f8ae4f7b08edf3430bd4b4aa567d3d05ec0e615","tid":648414,"uid":96561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:08:22.000Z","msg":"最近學鋼琴，本書有兩條問題唔明<br />\n1. In 3/4 time, a quarter note gets _____ counts.<br />\n2. In 6/8 time, a quarter note gets _____ counts.<br />\n<br />\n第一條我諗答案係3counts , 因為3/4 time = 3個quarter note。 <br />\n但係我問其他朋友，有人答1 counts。咁究竟係點？<br />\n<br />\n第二條我係本書其中一首歌嘅tips見到 quarter note 係 6/8 time gets two counts. <br />\n我睇埋首歌，大約理解成，雖然1個quarter note等於2個eighth note, 但係都唔可以係一個小節寫3個quarter note。 <br />\n但係又有朋友答3 counts。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望有樂理高手解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"909ca51bfdbe62dfa386d5424246088f21cfa433","tid":648414,"uid":44323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:11:14.000Z","msg":"唔撚明咩count 唔count , 是咪1 同 1.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d30f39f037bbea2773a5c5905a96f67a7825e21e","tid":648414,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:11:58.000Z","msg":"1count定義係乜"},{"pid":"6af6aa6a5e0117114e7f6bc0e431508bda2bc86e","tid":648414,"uid":96561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d30f39f037bbea2773a5c5905a96f67a7825e21e","tid":648414,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:11:58.000Z","msg":"1count定義係乜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:15:37.000Z","msg":"我諗係拍子掛..."},{"pid":"4ae112accd88d6aef12483f9625d9918792cb44a","tid":648414,"uid":96561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:17:15.000Z","msg":"本書個名叫 John w. Schaum piano course B-the blue book"},{"pid":"d5d95734c1493f9b4e8fc0ca806e60feead168c8","tid":648414,