"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:34:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>數碼琴自學一問,大家通常係學哂樂理先去摸琴定一路去彈歌再去摸樂理</blockquote>我依家就係邊學琴邊學樂理<br />\n但係就卡住咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本身自學緊結他,大概明個原理,我係卡唔知學邊方面既野好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3ca1de7b508439e31d61b884f70796c15eb8ab8","tid":648414,"uid":154447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:38:29.000Z","msg":"1. One<br />\n2. Half<br />\n<br />\n人地係問緊一個quarter"},{"pid":"ecaaa768d780a59844fbc6494417fb4da3e2167d","tid":648414,"uid":75870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b78c52071835cecc1c881b428b17938b303b16ad","tid":648414,"uid":96561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"686d24f342a199c20dcb92933e857e4b0912abac","tid":648414,"uid":75870,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:24:30.000Z","msg":"睇左你本野 p.15<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.scribd.com/doc/183566712/John-W-Schaum-Piano-Course-B-The-Blue-Book\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.scribd.com%2Fdoc%2F183566712%2FJohn-W-Schaum-Piano-Course-B-The-Blue-Book&d=CKP6R7xOsIMcEqWMGR%2ByKP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=115f5183\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.scribd.com/doc/183566712/John-W-Schaum-Piano-Course-B-The-Blue-Book</a><br />\n6/8佢數subdivisions 即係一個measure數6下 所以quarter note = 2 counts in 6/8<br />\n<br />\nDUM撚左本野去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:34:27.000Z","msg":"唔明你意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:38:51.000Z","msg":"6/8 = 6 eighth notes = 6 counts (1 2 3 4 5 6)<br />\n1 quarter note = 2 eighth notes = 2 counts (<strong>1 2</strong> 3 4 5 6)<br />\n<br />\n3/4 = 3 quarter notes = 3 counts (1 2 3)<br />\n1 quarter note = 1 count (<strong>1</strong> 2 3)"},{"pid":"51b547203f926edb4746b3ff7ece344aa3ea0461","tid":648414,"uid":5777,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f8ae4f7b08edf3430bd4b4aa567d3d05ec0e615","tid":648414,"uid":96561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:08:22.000Z","msg":"最近學鋼琴，本書有兩條問題唔明<br />\n1. In 3/4 time, a quarter note gets _____ counts.<br />\n2. In 6/8 time, a quarter note gets _____ counts.<br />\n<br />\n第一條我諗答案係3counts , 因為3/4 time = 3個quarter note。 <br />\n但係我問其他朋友，有人答1 counts。咁究竟係點？<br />\n<br />\n第二條我係本書其中一首歌嘅tips見到 quarter note 係 6/8 time gets two counts. <br />\n我睇埋首歌，大約理解成，雖然1個quarter note等於2個eighth note, 但係都唔可以係一個小節寫3個quarter note。 <br />\n但係又有朋友答3 counts。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望有樂理高手解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等我講人話<br />\n 34 拍子 下面個4指 4分音符為一拍 咁佢問一個4分音符等於幾拍 咁咪一拍囉<br />\n<br />\n68 拍 8分音符為一拍 咁一個4分音符等於兩個8分 所以咪等於兩拍"},{"pid":"606d83cc837b1b03dae90251383b24b1636369ef","tid":648414,"uid":96561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51b547203f926edb4746b3ff7ece344aa3ea0461","tid":648414,"uid":5777,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f8ae4f7b08edf3430bd4b4aa567d3d05ec0e615","tid":648414,"uid":96561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:08:22.000Z","msg":"最近學鋼琴，本書有兩條問題唔明<br />\n1. In 3/4 time, a quarter note gets _____ counts.<br />\n2. In 6/8 time, a quarter note gets _____ counts.<br />\n<br />\n第一條我諗答案係3counts , 因為3/4 time = 3個quarter note。 <br />\n但係我問其他朋友，有人答1 counts。咁究竟係點？<br />\n<br />\n第二條我係本書其中一首歌嘅tips見到 quarter note 係 6/8 time gets two counts. <br />\n我睇埋首歌，大約理解成，雖然1個quarter note等於2個eighth note, 但係都唔可以係一個小節寫3個quarter note。 <br />\n但係又有朋友答3 counts。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望有樂理高手解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等我講人話<br />\n 34 拍子 下面個4指 4分音符為一拍 咁佢問一個4分音符等於幾拍 咁咪一拍囉<br />\n<br />\n68 拍 8分音符為一拍 咁一個4分音符等於兩個8分 所以咪等於兩拍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T17:07:31.000Z","msg":"哦！明白了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2ab5ca0907275b391e458ef1e54aa2edf3ccabd","tid":648414,"uid":96561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T17:08:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. One<br />\n2. Half<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">人地係問緊一個quarter</span></blockquote><br />\nThx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ea33fcfddeeb03274786e864c68726b9e1dc2db","tid":648414,"uid":121111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:31:34.000Z","msg":"1. ans:1<br />\n3/4拍意思係每小節有3拍，每拍係一個4分音（quarter note)<br />\n所以答案係1<br />\n<br />\n2. ans:2/3<br />\n有人會問3/4拍同6/8拍唔係一樣都係有6個8分音符咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為3x (1/4)=3/4=6x(1/8)<br />\n其實6/8係2拍，唔係6拍<br />\n只係將1拍再分成3小拍<br />\n所以每拍係等於3個8分符<br />\n3x(1/8)=3/8=1.5x(1/4)<br />\n即係6/8拍係以一個dotted quarter note為1拍<br />\n以上兩種節奏分別係單拍子(simple rhythm)同複拍子(compound rhythm)<br />\n單拍子以普通音符為1拍，分拍係1半1半咁<br />\ne.g. 1個4分音符=2個8分音符=4個16分音符，如此類推<br />\n複拍子以附點音符為1拍<br />\n以題目為們，1拍係一個dotted quarter note<br />\n所以ans=quarter note/dotted quarter note=2/3<br />\n<br />\n利申:今年入APA鋼琴系"},{"pid":"b43149ff4c17f49d58081993697bf5332afeb7c5","tid":648414,"uid":121111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:45:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. ans:1<br />\n3/4拍意思係每小節有3拍，每拍係一個4分音（quarter note)<br />\n所以答案係1<br />\n<br />\n2. ans:2/3<br />\n有人會問3/4拍同6/8拍唔係一樣都係有6個8分音符咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為3x (1/4)=3/4=6x(1/8)<br />\n其實6/8係2拍，唔係6拍<br />\n只係將1拍再分成3小拍<br />\n所以每拍係等於3個8分符<br />\n3x(1/8)=3/8=1.5x(1/4)<br />\n即係6/8拍係以一個dotted quarter note為1拍<br />\n以上兩種節奏分別係單拍子(simple rhythm)同複拍子(compound rhythm)<br />\n單拍子以普通音符為1拍，分拍係1半1半咁<br />\ne.g. 1個4分音符=2個8分音符=4個16分音符，如此類推<br />\n複拍子以附點音符為1拍<br />\n以題目為<span style=\"color: red;\">例</span>，1拍係一個dotted quarter note<br />\n所以ans=quarter note/dotted quarter note=2/3<br />\n<br />\n利申:今年入APA鋼琴系</blockquote>"}]}